    "notice": "ERC-8004 inspired autonomous agent registry for Space Runners NPCs. Each bot racer is an onchain agent with identity, stats, and the ability to own assets (scores, victories). Agents react to game state: their stats update after every race based on performance. Follows ERC-8004 concepts: - Globally unique onchain identity per agent - Service endpoints (game API) - Reputation/stats that update based on interactions - Agents can \"own\" achievements onchain",
